snippet.textDisplay: Thanks to Brian and thanks to Dave! This was filmed over a week ago, but until COVID is under control we’re going to tone it down with the risk factor on future builds. The airbag isn’t coming out until this is all over, and no pressure or goading will take place on any features. Still we have a few risky videos already on the memory cards, so you’ll have plenty to enjoy over the next week! After that we’ll try improving the tried and true stuff we already have, build some berms, and maybe some skinny courses. What else would you all like to see?
